headline: How Hershey, United Airlines, and Others Unseated AI to Become the New Stock Market Darlings
summary: In July 2024 and early 2025 there were similar moves away from risky assets as the market broadened out. What’s different this time.

summary: Ball Corporation (NYSE:BALL) is included among the 10 Most Profitable Undervalued Stocks to Buy On February 5, 2026, Citi analyst Anthony Pettinari raised his price target on Ball Corporation to $74 from $67 and reiterated a Buy rating, citing strong fourth-quarter results and what the firm described as a compelling outlook for 2026 and 2027.
